            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> figlio <rs
                            key="#Clerical_concubinage">della <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage"
                                >fu <name ref="Fraginberga">Fraimberga</name></persName></rs> e la
                        moglie <persName><name ref="Bonadonna">Bonadonna</name></persName> figlia di
                                <persName><name ref="Melus">Melo</name></persName>, con il consenso
                        del marito, interrogata dal <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">giudice
                            del sacro palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name
                                ref="Sigefredus">Sighifridi</name></persName>, vendono a
                                <persName><name ref="Bonatus">Bonato</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Bonicus">Bonico</name></persName>, un
                        appezzamento di terra, quod est vinea et oliveto, posto in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/633">Gello</placeName> prope la <rs
                            key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3110"
                            key="#Churches">San Bartolomeo</orgName>, <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> unum caput cum uno
                        latere in via et simitula, aliud caput con terra di <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Vitalis"
                            >Vitale</name></persName>, aliud latus in classo, per una misura
                        complessiva di 32 staia con tutte le sue dipendenze, ricevendo <rs
                            key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">meritum nappum argentum</rs> pro 400
                        soldi. Chiedono al <rs key="#Notary #Writer">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alberto</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                                sottoscrittori: Sighifridi iudex sacri palatii, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                    ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Garofalus">Garofalo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                    ref="Villanus">Villano</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Dominicus">Domenico</name></persName>. </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
